2. cs.SD (Software Engineering) - The paper mentions the use of an algorithm called Parallel Iterative Local Search, which is a software engineering technique. 
3. cs.SOC (Social and Economic Networks) - The study involves analyzing voting patterns in the European Parliament, which can be seen as a type of economic network. 
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper discusses the use of community detection algorithms and graph partitioning techniques, which are topics commonly studied in data structures and algorithms. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper mentions the use of weighted signed links, which can be seen as a type of machine learning technique for analyzing network data.
